            "text": "<p>When I first began my journey, no one believed that I could create something meaningful. But I knew that with faith and perseverance, every challenge could be turned into an opportunity. I didn’t just want to sell T-shirts; I wanted to share the message of Christ with everyone, helping them feel the peace and love that faith brings.</p><p>At the beginning, I had just a small amount of savings and an old, worn-out computer. Everything seemed uncertain, but one thing was clear: I wanted to create a space where people could find hope and comfort through T-shirts with Bible verses and messages of love and salvation.</p>",
