            "enable_custom_title_size": false,
            "custom_title_size": 32,
            "text": "<p><br/>The work wasn’t easy. I had to do everything myself: from designing the products, sourcing materials, to building the store. In those early days, I often felt alone. Long nights spent in front of the screen, tweaking every detail on the website, worrying over each small order. But in my heart, I kept praying, believing that each T-shirt would be a reminder of God’s love and care.<br/>Then one day, it happened—my first order came in. I remember crying. Not because it was a big sale or because I had finally made a sale, but because I felt the presence of God in every step of the way. Every T-shirt I created was not just a product, but a mission.<br/></p>",
